# Pattern 31: Bot Niche Market

This pattern compares three chatbot/mini-app niches (subscription parsers, high-ticket bespoke B2B TMA, and premium AI LLM Oracles) over a 3-month horizon to evaluate the fastest path to profitability.

## Scope Declaration

```catala
declaration scope Pattern31BotNicheMarket:
  # Constants
  input parser_build_time content integer
  input parser_monthly_pay content money
  input tma_build_time content integer
  input tma_project_price content money
  input ai_build_time content integer
  input ai_monthly_pay content money

  # State variables
  input time_spent content integer
  input niche_parsers content integer
  input b2b_mini_apps content integer
  input ai_oracles content integer
  input accumulated_profit content money

  # Action choices
  input action_build_parser content boolean
  input action_build_tma content boolean
  input action_build_ai content boolean
  input action_monthly_cycle content boolean

  # Updated state variables
  output new_time_spent content integer
  output new_niche_parsers content integer
  output new_b2b_mini_apps content integer
  output new_ai_oracles content integer
  output new_accumulated_profit content money
```

## Rules and Definitions

```catala
scope Pattern31BotNicheMarket:
  definition new_time_spent equals
    if action_build_parser and time_spent < 480 then
      time_spent + parser_build_time
    else if action_build_tma and time_spent < 480 then
      time_spent + tma_build_time
    else if action_build_ai and time_spent < 480 then
      time_spent + ai_build_time
    else
      time_spent

  definition new_niche_parsers equals
    if action_build_parser and time_spent < 480 then
      niche_parsers + 1
    else
      niche_parsers

  definition new_b2b_mini_apps equals
    if action_build_tma and time_spent < 480 then
      b2b_mini_apps + 1
    else
      b2b_mini_apps

  definition new_ai_oracles equals
    if action_build_ai and time_spent < 480 then
      ai_oracles + 1
    else
      ai_oracles

  definition new_accumulated_profit equals
    if action_build_parser and time_spent < 480 then
      accumulated_profit + parser_monthly_pay
    else if action_build_tma and time_spent < 480 then
      accumulated_profit + tma_project_price
    else if action_build_ai and time_spent < 480 then
      accumulated_profit + ai_monthly_pay
    else if action_monthly_cycle and time_spent < 480 then
      accumulated_profit 
      + (decimal of niche_parsers * parser_monthly_pay) 
      + (decimal of ai_oracles * ai_monthly_pay)
    else
      accumulated_profit
```
